{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "storyku-collection-v1",
    "name": "Storyku API",
    "description": "API Specification untuk Storyku — Platform Manajemen Cerita\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}`\n\n**Stack:** Go · Echo v4 · PostgreSQL\n\n---\n\n### Setup\n1. Set variable `base_url` = `http://localhost:8080`\n2. Jalankan migration SQL (`001_create_tables.sql`)\n3. Jalankan server: `air` atau `go run ./cmd/main.go`\n\n### Flow Penggunaan\n```\n1. GET  /categories       → ambil list category\n2. GET  /tags             → ambil list tag (buat baru bila perlu)\n3. POST /stories          → buat story, kirim category_id & tag_ids\n4. POST /stories/:id/chapters  → tambah chapter\n```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "category_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID category — auto-set setelah Create Category"
    },
    {
      "key": "tag_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID tag — auto-set setelah Create Tag"
    },
    {
      "key": "story_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID story — auto-set setelah Create Story"
    },
    {
      "key": "chapter_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "UUID chapter — auto-set setelah Add Chapter"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Dashboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil semua data dashboard dalam satu request:\n- Summary (total stories, published, draft, chapters, categories, tags)\n- Stories per category\n- Stories per status (publish vs draft)\n- Top 5 tags terbanyak dipakai\n- 5 story terbaru\n- 5 chapter terbaru"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"dashboard data retrieved successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"total_stories\": 10,\n    \"total_chapters\": 50,\n    \"total_categories\": 5,\n    \"total_tags\": 10\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
